The R8 Revolver delivers a highly accurate and powerful round at the expense of a lengthy trigger-pull. Firing rapidly by fanning the hammer may be the best option when point-blank stopping power is required. It has been custom painted to resemble acanthus engravings and a marble grip. Opulence in the palm of your hand
Sticker: ENCE (Gold) | Paris 2023, Anubis (Gold), FaZe Clan (Gold) | Paris 2023, BLAST.tv (Gold) | Paris 2023

Powerful and reliable, the AK-47 is one of the most popular assault rifles in the world. It is most deadly in short, controlled bursts of fire. It has been custom painted with a Cubism depiction of Elite Crew Ts sneaking up A-long on Dust II. "Everything you can imagine is real"
Sticker: Tamara (Holo), Ivette (Holo), Kimberly (Holo), Sherry (Holo)

Essentially a box that bullets come out of, the MAC-10 SMG boasts a high rate of fire, with poor spread accuracy and high recoil as trade-offs. A woman in teal, believed to be iso onna, stands before koi fish and crashing waves on this custom painted MAC-10. Beauty begets bloodshed

As expensive as it is powerful, the Desert Eagle is an iconic pistol that is difficult to master but surprisingly accurate at long range. It has been covered in a metallic foil stamped with a digital disruptive pattern.
Sticker: Team Liquid (Holo) | Stockholm 2021, Team Liquid (Holo) | Stockholm 2021, Team Liquid (Holo) | Stockholm 2021, Team Liquid (Holo) | Stockholm 2021

The R8 Revolver delivers a highly accurate and powerful round at the expense of a lengthy trigger-pull. It has been painted using a spider web-patterned hydrographic over a red base coat and finished with a semi-gloss topcoat. Be careful where you walk, you never know where the web is spread
Versatile but expensive, the German-made MP7 SMG is the perfect choice for high-impact close-range combat. It has been covered in white logo decals over a red and black hydrographic. Space for rent
